task.summary: Adding a connector to handle cross server actions. Will be shifting towards docker.
Made the connector the one to check if a server is up, instead of having the server itself ping, it will check the database. Appears to be working better.
Connector can now send commands to running servers. Will also auto restart a server if found to be out of date.
Now previous changes should work properly.
Connector has Load balancing. Will start servers if there are none. Additionally, added GlobalChat Command. /gc Will check further.
Connector now properly detects player count on server.
Added Staff chat and fixed global chat.
Command "server reload/restart" will now issue a Restart command with Connector.
Got some ground work laid out for Arcade plugin. For now will run as a test server.
Fixed a bit. Working on getting Teams and Kits implemented (will have team specific kits available as well)
More groundwork laid out for the Arcade plugin. Working on Spleef as first game type.
Having issues adding arcade command to the GlobalMain..
Got basic Spleef working. Just a few issues that need to be cleaned up. Null pointer exceptions being thrown.
Spleef is working from what I can tell now. Will need to invest in a way to test multiple accounts on the server.
